# 11. Trust System

Every product page should contain:

Contact

Privacy Policy

Refund Policy

Shipping Policy

Terms of Service

Customers buy trust before they buy products.

---

# 12. Payment Rules

Current payment provider:

PayPal only.

Do NOT build:

Shopping cart

Order system

User accounts

Inventory management

These belong to future versions.

The first goal:

One successful payment.

---

