# 14. Scalability Principles

Today's product:

Hair Dryer Brush

Tomorrow:

Pet Steam Brush

Next month:

Desk Accessories

The system should support unlimited products.

Only product content changes.

Architecture stays the same.

---

# 15. AI Collaboration Rules

AI should always prioritize:

Maintainability

↓

Readability

↓

Reusability

↓

Performance

↓

Visual consistency

↓

Conversion

Never generate code simply to demonstrate technical ability.

Generate code that a real startup would maintain.

---

# 16. Coding Style

Write clean code.

Prefer composition over duplication.

Avoid magic numbers.

Use descriptive variable names.

Keep functions short.

Keep components focused.

Readable code is better than clever code.

